This replication script use on beloww situation:

- use My SQL database version 5.7
- use mysql on a container that config files are volumes

Usage:

A) On master db server:
1- set variables on env file according to your project
2- run "bash run-master.sh"

A) On slave db server:
1- set variables on env file according to your project
2- run "bash run-slave.sh"